flowchart TD
    S([Student]) -->|Login/Register| Auth[Authentication System]
    I([Instructor]) -->|Login/Register| Auth
    A([Admin]) -->|Login| Auth

    S -->|Browses Course Catalog| DB[(SQLite Database)]
    S -->|Enrolls in Course| DB
    S -->|Views Hybrid Lessons| Media[Lesson Content Engine]
    S -->|Submits Quiz Answers| Eval[Assessment Engine]
    
    Eval -->|Updates Progress/Score| DB
    Eval -->|Issues Request| Cert[Certificate Generator]
    Cert -->|Returns Image & UUID| S

    I -->|Uploads Course Details| DB
    I -->|Embeds YouTube URLs| Media
    
    A -->|Views Platform Metrics| DB
    A -->|Manages User Roles| DB
